name: Tompkinsville, KY
tagline: The small town at the heart of Monroe County.
body:
### Oh no! This isn't what you were expecting.
The domain registration for cityoftompkinsville.com had expired.
After seeing this domain posted across various sites (such as the [BRADD city officials directory](http://www.bradd.org/index.php/officials-directory/monroe-county/43-city-of-tompkinsville-officials.html)) we decided to renew the domain and build a proper website for our town.

We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused you, and will ensure that future searches for information on our fair city will be met swiftly and accurately.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
